# Data Visualization Project

## Project Overview

This project presents data insights through interactive dashboards and visualizations. The objective was to transform analytical findings into clear and meaningful visual stories that support business decision-making.

## Objectives

* Visualize key performance indicators (KPIs).
* Communicate insights effectively.
* Identify trends, patterns, and opportunities.
* Support decision-making through dashboards.

## Tools Used

* Microsoft Excel
* Pivot Tables
* Pivot Charts
* Dashboard Design

## Dashboard Features

* KPI Summary Cards
* Interactive Filters/Slicers
* Trend Analysis
* Category Performance Analysis
* Business Insights Visualization

📊 Key Insights Discovered:
✅ Generated over $1.26M in revenue from 1,200 orders.
✅ Chairs emerged as the top revenue-generating product.
✅ Email and Instagram were among the strongest referral channels driving sales.
✅ Delivered orders accounted for the largest share of transactions, reflecting strong order fulfillment performance.
✅ Revenue trends revealed peak sales periods that can guide future marketing and inventory planning.

💡 Recommendations:
• Invest more in the highest-performing referral channels.
• Prioritize inventory for top-selling products to prevent stock shortages.
• Leverage peak sales periods for targeted campaigns and promotions.
• Continue improving customer experience to maintain high delivery success rates.

